  "text": "Urine samples were collected as described [CITATION_1] . Creatinine was determined with the Creatinine Companion (Exocell, Philadelphia, PA, USA). Samples corresponding to 1 lg creatinine were analysed by SDS-PAGE, followed by immunoblotting or Coomassie staining (Gel code Blue, Thermo Scientific, Rockford, IL, USA). Albumin concentrations were determined using a mouse albumin ELISA Quantification kit (Bethyl Labs, Montgomery, TX, USA).",
